{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ccfdd01999","title":"九兵团全部开到徐济线整训","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c5d240e956","index":0,"year":1950,"month":9,"day":8,"articleId":"ccfdd01999"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji29","name":"毛泽东全集第29卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/29-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji29":{"comments":[{"id":"d533dee3b6","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ccfdd01999","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东在华东军区1950年9月5日关于九兵团北调执行办法的报告上写的批语。"},{"id":"7c5b617b27","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ccfdd01999","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"徐济线，指徐州至济南的铁路，即今京沪线一段。"}],"contents":[{"id":"bf7a168fc7","type":"title","text":"九兵团全部开到徐济线整训","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ccfdd01999"},{"id":"d533dee3b6","type":"paragraph","text":"九兵团全部可以统于十月底开到徐济线，十一月中句开始整训。该兵团在徐济线整训期间仍归华东建制，唯装备及整训方针计划受军委直接指挥为适宜。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ccfdd01999"},{"id":"7c5b617b27","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ccfdd01999"},{"id":"4b9dacc311","type":"paragraph","text":"九月八日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ccfdd01999"}],"page":{"id":"de87b480f4","publicationId":"maoquanji29","articleId":"ccfdd01999","start":136,"end":136}}}},"__N_SSG":true}